  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Empty containers/vectors are represented by an empty string. Therefore, lists of empty containers are always `0x 00 00 00 00`, regardless of the length of the list. As a data structure that's always empty is pretty useless anyway, I think it's safe to just disallow them.",
