    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Maybe worth pointing out that this extends to *any* composite of **only** empty Vectors and Containers always serialize to the empty string (under the new SOS layout).\r\n\r\nI can't immediately come up with any compelling use case for empty Vectors/Containers which makes me lean towards disallowing it in the spec.  Maybe worth surfacing in the next call if only to bring this to peoples attention in case someone comes up with something worthwhile.",
