    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The only application would be to have a \"Null\" object that can be used in a (to be added) Option type that would allow nullable fields. While this is not needed inside the spec, it would allow SSZ to also be used in networking, and seems a fairly easy change.\r\nThen we could disallow any empty containers except for the \"Null\" object.",
