    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Sounds good to me; lists of empty containers/vectors do break the invariant that SSZ serialization is injective within each type (ie. two different things of the same SSZ type always serialize to different values), so banning empty containers/vectors and making the empty string be the serialization of Null makes sense.",
